            "owasp": "A05:2021",
            "cwe": "CWE-693",
            "impact": "Missing Permissions-Policy may allow unnecessary browser capabilities to remain available.",
            "remediation": "Configure Permissions-Policy to explicitly restrict unnecessary browser capabilities.",
